{"tid":23354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獅子山頂行扁帶　洋漢險墮崖","createTime":"2016-12-05T01:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T01:52:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ce744bbecb264bfc3d701082ec2fa23b33394a","tid":23354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19855460&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19855460%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161205&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=e3f7f779\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19855460%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161205&h=257f96bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19855460&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161205</a><br />\n<br />\n獅子山頂行扁帶　洋漢險墮崖<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■來自墨西哥的Ricardo昨於獅子山行高空扁帶，吸引市民圍觀。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】7名高空扁帶發燒友昨連續第二天挑戰獅子山，在495米高空，踏着一條闊約一吋的扁帶，從一個山𥧌走到另一山𥧌，過百圍觀者屏息靜氣，情緒被他們驚險的一舉一動牽引着，因做足安全措施全程有驚無險。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■發燒友失手滑倒，幸有安全帶保命，過程驚險萬分。<br />\n<br />\n逾百市民圍觀<br />\n<br />\n昨晨9時許，7名發燒友上山準備，身上扣好安全帶，將扁帶扣好在兩𥧌岩壁間，一名法籍男留學生一馬當先，只見他赤腳緩行，雙手張開協助平衡，過百市民圍觀，法籍男曾多次失手，幸有安全帶保命不致墮崖，但市民已嚇得冷汗直標，驚叫聲響徹山谷。<br />\n<br />\n來自墨西哥的Ricardo（29歲）表示，5年前來港，做繙譯工作，來港不久則認識一班高空扁帶發燒友，他開始投入這項運動，初時在幾呎高地方練習平衡，其後轉移至柴灣歌連臣角海峽及東龍島等地。他表示，獅子山遍佈攀山人士留下的釘扣，適合索好扁帶，他認為獅子山位置頗佳，天氣又好，所以各人十分享受。<br />\n<br />\n高空扁帶（Slackline）運動在外國流行多年，參加者多是攀石高手，講求手腳協調、平衡力及膽量。扁帶質料以人造纖維為主，闊度約一至兩吋，厚度約一吋，能承受約數百公斤的重量。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;世衞設救援隊名冊保質素<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;居港英漢跑星洲渣馬亡"},{"pid":"efac16b4e75b59b10c78a6b30a5c9312afe88f4e","tid":23354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161205/280pix/05la4p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161205%2F280pix%2F05la4p4.jpg&h=08d4d44e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"436dedc2e571b1550354481978c817e162eee53f","tid":23354,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"有安全帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f68e11fe2b88f265ddf5f4bb488c8ae7c4bd27","tid":23354,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有安全帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15beece9356ea48ddcb5a03ae0575ce5fe6c2bb","tid":23354,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:34:55.000Z","msg":"咁押韻"},{"pid":"02c7dea048b59e9021335b347853ac483d45c46f","tid":23354,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"其實唔難"}]}